sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User as AuthenticatedUser
participant Client as WebClient
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant AuthMW as AuthMiddleware
participant PermMW as PermissionMiddleware
participant RoleApi as RolePermissionApi
participant PermSvc as PermissionService
participant RoleDb as MongoRoleUserRole
participant Redis as RedisPermissionCache
participant Domain as TargetDomainService
User->>Client: Thuc hien thao tac private
Client->>Gateway: HTTP request + JWT
Gateway->>AuthMW: verifyAccessToken
alt JWT sai/het han
  AuthMW-->>Client: 401
else JWT hop le
  AuthMW-->>Gateway: req.user ok
  Gateway->>PermMW: map action theo method+path
  PermMW->>RoleApi: POST /api/permissions/check
  RoleApi->>PermSvc: checkPermission(user,server,action)
  PermSvc->>Redis: GET permissions:<user>:<server>
  alt Cache miss
    PermSvc->>RoleDb: Join UserRole + Role permissions
    PermSvc->>Redis: SET cache
  end
  alt Allowed
    PermMW-->>Gateway: pass
    Gateway->>Domain: Proxy to target service
    Domain-->>Client: 2xx success
  else Denied/context thieu/role api loi
    PermMW-->>Client: 403/400
  end
end
